Subject: [PATCH] Fix stop button + implement microphone recording
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Stop button:
- Move TransportBtn out of Transport component body — React was
  recreating the component type on every render, causing unmount/
  remount on state changes which swallowed clicks mid-transition
- Stop button now correctly disabled when already stopped
- All transport buttons use stable component reference

Record button:
- Add src/engine/recorder.ts: getUserMedia + MediaRecorder wrapper
  startRecording() opens mic stream; stopRecording() returns AudioBuffer
  decoded from the captured blob (webm/opus or webm fallback)
- handleRecord arms mic if a track is armed, calls startPlayback so
  existing clips play back during recording (overdub)
- handleStop stops MediaRecorder, decodes blob, inserts clip at the
  beat position where recording started on the armed track
- Error toasts for: no track armed, mic permission denied, device error
- Record button pulses red while capturing; play/skip disabled during record
